name: SHEBUSA
tag_list: e-commerce, made-to-measure, made-to-order, customization, luxury, apparel, fashion, accessories
overview:
Shebusa is the experience for buying unique & customized made to measure personal luxury goods produced by European Master Craftsmen.

Shebusa offers to its customers - individual active women - unique and customized made to measure personal luxury goods such as clothes and accessories. The current offer includes: business suits (jackets, trousers, skirts), dresses, shirts, Chanel like jackets, Fur coats, Handbags and Small Maroquinerie, as well as Belts and Luxury Hats.

The products are unique, made to order, exclusively produced by European Master Craftsmen. Shebusa focuses on one-to-one service strategy through its webstore and brick and mortar concept stores.
